      "para_id": "Q001687.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ig-alima , the beloved child of Ninĝirsu , his master , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad dedicated this ( statutette ) for his well-being ."
    }
